sentences: He is a member of the International Contemporary Ensemble and Wet by the ICE, Yarn/Wire, the Donaueschingen Musiktage Festival, the Jerome Foundation's Emerging Artist Program, and was a 2014 Artist-in-Residence at Issue Project Room in Brooklyn, New York.
Evans performed at the 2016 Kanye West x Adidas fashion show in New York City.
In 2011 Evans founded the label More is More Records.
